headline: Island Inspired Collaboration: SPAM® Brand Creates Exclusive Collectible Cans in celebration of Disney's "Lilo & Stitch" Live-Action Movie
summary: Just as Stitch found his perfect home in Hawai'i, the SPAM® brand has found the perfect collaboration with Disney's upcoming live-action "Lilo & Stitch" movie releasing only in theaters May 23. Now on shelves, fans can collect three Hawaiian-inspired limited-edition SPAM® brand cans featuring artwork from the beloved movie.
